                <mxCell id="118" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 32px;&quot;&gt;Vhexxa&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;is a platform where you can rent vehicles!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;and I mean it any type of vehicles, cars, motors, boats, yachts or even halicopters hmm...&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;if you could find it.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;In this platform you... yes you can rent your vehicles besdie the platform owned vehicles you can rent them&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;as an indivisual or a company&lt;br&gt;we take either a percent or you can take one of our plans where you just pay certine amount of money&lt;br&gt;instead of percent and save more mony.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
